ened%20in%20Rajkot%20in%20the%20third%20India%20vs%20England%20Test%2C%20there%20were%20emotional%20scenes%20as%20his%20father%20and%20wife%20could%20not%20stop%20their%20tears.%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20repaid%20their%20faith%20with%20a%20confident%20innings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Frohit-sharma-disgusted-as-on-song-sarfaraz-khan-departs-after-mix-up-with-ravindra-jadeja-watch-5063064%23pfrom%3Dhome-ndtv_lateststories%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERohit%20Disgusted%20As%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20Departs%20After%20Mix-up%20With%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20Khan%20scored%20a%2048-ball%20half-century%20-%20the%20fastest%20by%20an%20Indian%20in%20the%20post-independence%20era%20-%20before%20departing%20at%2062%20after%20a%20horrible%20run%20out%20mix%20up%20with%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-ravindra-jadeja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20captain%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F857-rohit-sharma-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERohit%20Sharma%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20frustrated%20after%20the%20dismissal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERead%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-england-2024%2Fsarfaraz-khan-run-out-ravindra-jadeja-at-fault-anil-kumble-says-this-about-his-decision-making-5063368%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESarfaraz%20Run%20Out%3A%20Jadeja%20At%20Fault%3F%20Kumble%20Says%20This%20About%20His%20%26quot%3BDecision-Making%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20Khan%20opened%20up%20on%20his%20dismissal%20at%20the%20end%20of%20day's%20play.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20times%20there%20is%20miscommunication%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20game.%20Sometimes%20you%20get%20run%20out.%20Such%20kind%20of%20things%20happen%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20%C2%A0said%20in%20the%20post-match%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESarfaraz%20Khan%20added%20that%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20helped%20him%20throughout%20his%20innings.%20%26quot%3BI%20talked%20to%20him%20at%20lunch%20time.%20I%20am%20that%20type%20of%20batter%20who%20like%20to%20talk%20while%20batting%20about%20what%20is%20going%20on.%20So%2C%20I%20told%20Jadeja%20to%20keep%20talking%20to%20me%20while%20I%20bat.%20He%20supported%20me%20a%20lot%20today%20and%20spoke%20to%20me%20at%20lunchtime%2C%26quot%3B%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20told%20me%20how%20the%20debutants%20feel%20and%20how%20he%20felt%20as%20a%20debutant.%20I%20was%20a%20bit%20nervous%2C%20especially%20when%20I%20played%20my%20first%20sweep%20and%20missed%20it.%20But%20he%20told%20me%20to%20take%20some%20time%20and%20it%20would%20be%20easy.%20I%20listened%20to%20him%20and%20tried%20implementing%20it.%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20what%20Jadeja%20said%20on%20the%20run%20out%2C%20Sarfaraz%20said%3A%20%26quot%3BHe%20said%20there%20was%20a%20bit%20of%20miscommunication%2C%20but%20I%20said%20it's%20okay.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%20Sharma%20and%20Ravindra%20Jadeja%20made%20classical%20Test%20match%20hundreds%20while%20debutant%20Sarfaraz%20Khan%20announced%20his%20arrival%20on%20the%20big%20stage%20with%20a%20fluent%20half-century%20as%20India%20reached%20326%20for%20five%20at%20stumps%20on%20day%20one%20of%20the%20third%20Test%20against%20England%20in%20Rajkot%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20India%20reduced%20to%2033%20for%20three%20inside%20the%20first%20hour%20of%20play%2C%20Rohit%20(131%20off%20196)%20and%20Jadeja%20(110%20batting%20off%20212)%20steered%20the%20ship%20through%20choppy%20waters%20with%20a%20204-run%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20pair%20was%20separated%2C%20Sarfaraz%20(62%20off%2066)%20scored%20the%20joint%20fastest%20fifty%20by%20an%20Indi