part%20objecting%20to%20Haryana%20Police%20using%20drones%20in%20their%20territory%20and%20asking%20to%20refrain%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708003737000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15184857%2FThe-unemployment-situation.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fpakistan-india-farmer-shambhu-medical-cost%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Most%20farmers%20admitted%20at%20the%20Rajpura%20government%20hospital%20have%20lacerated%20wounds%20which%20take%20a%20long%20time%20to%20heal.%20These%20were%20sustained%20after%20Haryana%20police%20and%20security%20forces%20fired%20pellets%20and%20tear%20gas%20on%20them.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Fpakistan-india-farmer-shambhu-medical-cost%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Why%20Putin's%20backing%20for%20Biden%20is%20not%20what%20it%20seems%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1708003460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FCD69%2Fproduction%2F_132658525_fa48940bb0c64cdb960d66317b63c2941887a46f0_99_3883_21851000x563.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68303231%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Had%20he%20backed%20a%20Trump%20presidency%2C%20it%20would%20have%20been%20a%20bigger%20gift%20for%20Joe%20Biden%2C%20says%20Steve%20Rosenberg.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A54%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68303231%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68303231.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-68303231.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mahua%20Moitra%20Summoned%20By%20Probe%20Agency%20In%20Foreign%20Exchange%20Violation%20Case%22%2C%22conten