D%20Abdullah%20told%20reporters.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CI%20think%20that%20elections%20in%20both%20states%20(Jammu%20and%20Kashmir)%20will%20be%20held%20with%20the%20parliamentary%20elections%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbdullah%E2%80%99s%20decision%20has%20come%20after%20a%20number%20of%20his%20party%20leaders%20in%20the%20Jammu%20region%20joined%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20last%20month.%20The%20delay%20in%20seat-sharing%20talks%20may%20have%20triggered%20the%20announcement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOn%20February%2012%2C%20Abdullah%20was%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fed-summons-farooq-abdullah-for-questioning-in-money-laundering-case-101707748254275.html%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Esummoned%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20questioning%20in%20a%20case%20related%20to%20alleged%20financial%20irregularities%20in%20the%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20Cricket%20Association.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESignificantly%2C%20the%20veteran%20Kashmir%20leader%20did%20not%20rule%20out%20returning%20to%20the%20NDA%20fold%20in%20the%20future.%20Abdullah%20had%20expressed%20his%20anguish%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20seat-sharing%20arrangement%2C%20and%20had%20hinted%20at%20forming%20a%20separate%20alliance%20in%20Kashmir.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Congress%E2%80%99s%20chief%20spokesperson%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20responded%20to%20Abdullah%E2%80%99s%20announcement%2C%20%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3ETalks%20are%20going%20on.%20Every%20party%20has%20their%20own%20limitations.%20National%20Conference%20and%20PDP%20have%20been%20a%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20and%20will%20continue%20to%20remain%20so.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbdullah%E2%80%99s%20flip-flop%20may%20come%20as%20a%20surprise%20as%20he%20has%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20advocates%20of%20forming%20a%20united%20opposition%20alliance.%20He%20has%20also%20been%20one%20of%20the%20most%20vocal%20opponents%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20recent%20times.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20a%20recent%20interview%2C%20Abdullah%20asserted%20that%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9Cto%20safeguard%20the%20nation%2C%20we%20must%20set%20aside%20our%20disagreements%20and%20prioritise%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20welfare.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHis%20son%20Omar%20Abdullah%20was%20a%20part%20of%20a%20Democracy%20Convention%20held%20in%20New%20Delhi%20where%20he%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20backsliding%20of%20democratic%20standards%20in%20India%20under%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20regime.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAbdullah%E2%80%99s%20exit%20will%20be%20yet%20another%20blow%20to%20the%20opposition%20efforts%20to%20come%20together%20ahead%20of%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20Jayant%20Chaudhary%E2%80%99s%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20recently%20left%20the%20alliance%20and%20joined%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party-led%20National%20Democratic%20Alliance.%20West%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20and%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20also%20exited%20INDIA%20after%20she%20declared%20that%20she%20will%20contest%20alone%20in%20West%20Bengal%20after%20her%20party%E2%80%99s%20talks%20with%20the%20Congress%20on%20seat-sharing%20collapsed.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20chief%20minister%20in%20Punjab%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20has%20also%20said%20that%20the%20party%20will%20contest%20all%2013%20seats%20in%20Punjab%2C%20leaving%20the%20Congress%20embarrassed.%20More%20recently%2C%20the%20talks%20between%20AAP%20and%20Congress%20also%20appear%20to%20be%20crashing%20after%20AAP%20only%20agreed%20to%20va