%20Donald%20Trump%20used%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.winred.com%2Fsave-america-joint-fundraising-committee%2Flp-hf-email-melania-valentine%5C%22%3EValentine's%20Day%20love%20letter%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20his%20wife%20Melania%20to%20ask%20supporters%20for%20money%20in%20a%20fund-raising%20email.%C2%A0In%20a%20campaign%20email%20sent%20Wednesday%20morning%2C%20Trump%20offered%20a%20''letter''%20with%20the%20subject%20line%2C%20''I%20love%20you%2C%20Melania!''%20In%20the%20letter%2C%20he%20hailed%20his%20wife%20for%20not%20leaving%20his%20side%20as%20he%20faced%20several%20civil%20and%20criminal%20charges.%C2%A0Notably%2C%20the%20Republican%20presidential%20nominee%20faces%2091%20felony%20counts%20across%20four%20federal%20and%20state%20indictments.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20letter%20reads%2C%20''Dear%20Melania%2C%20I%20LOVE%20YOU!%20Even%20after%20every%20single%20INDICTMENT%2C%20ARREST%2C%20and%20WITCH%20HUNT%2C%20you%20never%20left%20my%20side.%20You've%20always%20supported%20me%20through%20everything.%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20the%20man%20I%20am%20today%20without%20your%20guidance%2C%20kindness%2C%20and%20warmth.%20You%20will%20always%20mean%20the%20world%20to%20me%2C%20Melania!%20From%20your%20husband%20with%20love%2C%20Donald%20J%20Trump.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20letter%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EI%20don't%20know%20if%20Donald%20Trump%20actually%20wrote%20this%20heartfelt%20fundraising%20valentine%20to%20Melania%20for%20sticking%20by%20him%20through%20his%20indictments%2C%20but%20signing%20it%20%26quot%3BDonald%20J.%20Trump%26quot%3B%20at%20least%20makes%20it%20plausible.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FhQrcFIoef5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FhQrcFIoef5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Kyle%20Cheney%20(%40kyledcheney)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkyledcheney%2Fstatus%2F1757763611034841238%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2014%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20email%20also%20contains%20three%20%26quot%3BSEND%20YOUR%20LOVE%26quot%3B%20buttons%2C%20which%20bring%20supporters%20to%20a%20donation%20page%20that%20repeats%20the%20Valentine's%20Day%20message%2C%20and%20says%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20love%20Melania%2C%20I%20humbly%20ask%20you%20for%20you%20to%20leave%20her%20some%20kind%20words%20below!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20site%20suggests%20a%20minimum%20donation%20of%20%2420.24.%20However%2C%20those%20who%20regard%20him%20as%20the%20greatest%20president%20of%20all%20time%20can%20donate%C2%A0%2447%2C%C2%A0%24100%2C%20%24250%2C%20%24500%2C%20%241%2C000%2C%20%243%2C300%2C%20or%20any%20other%20amount.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMelania%20Trump%20had%20not%20been%20seen%20in%20public%20since%20her%20mother%20Amalija%20Knavs's%20death%20last%20month.%20However%2C%20she%20recently%20went%20with%20her%20husband%20to%20a%20gala%20at%20Mar-a-Lago%20on%20Saturday%20night.%20Donald%20and%20Melania%20Trump%20became%20engaged%20in%202004%2C%20and%20married%20in%20an%20extravagant%20ceremony%20at%20his%20Mar-a-Lago%20private%20club%20in%20January%202005.%20They%20welcomed%20their%20only%20child%20together%2C%20Barron%2C%20in%202006.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20Trump's%20main%20GOP%20challenger%2C%20Nikki%20Haley%2C%20offered%20her%20own%20Valentine's%20Day%20message%20to%20the%20former%20president.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Roses%20are%20red%2C%20violets%20are%20blue%2C%20I%20love%20dictators%2C%20and%20they%20love%20me%20too!%20Happy%20Valentine's%20Day%20from%20Donald%20Trump%20to%20dictators%20around%20the%20world!''%20Haley's%20presidential%20campaign%20wrote%20in%20an%20emailed%20statement%2C%20mocking%20the%20former%20president.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Over%20the%20years%2C%20Trump%20has%20professed%20his%20love%20for%20the%20world's%20most%20brutal%20dictators%20and%20praised%20their%20strength%20and%20leadership%20skills%2C''%20the%20statement%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707994440000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2017-01%2Fdonald-and-melania-trump_650x400_41484916430.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-uses-valentines-day-letter-to-melania-to-raise-money-for-his-campaign-5062780%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22In%20the%20letter%2C%20he%20hailed%20his%20wife%20for%20not%20leaving%20his%20side%20as%20he%20faced%20several%20civil%20and%20criminal%20charges.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-uses-valentines-day-letter-to-melania-to-raise-money-for-his-campaign-5062780%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-uses-valentines-day-letter-to-melania-to-raise-money-for-his-campaign-5062780%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-uses-valentines-day-letter-to-melania-to-raise-money-for-his-campaign-5062780%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Part%20of%20Secret%20Ballot'%3A%20How%20the%20Modi%20Govt%20Backed%20Electoral%20Bonds%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F10170626%2Fsyed-hussaini-HlLno-CSbq8-unsplash.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3EThe%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20February%2015%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-electoral-bonds-quash-anonymous%5C%22%3Epronounced%20electoral%20bonds%20unconstitutional%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20scheme%20was%20introduced%20by%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20in%202018%20and%20allowed%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%20To%20the%20Supreme%20Court%2C%20which%20heard%20pleas%20against%20the%20bonds%20last%20year%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20spoke%20of%20its%20justification%20for%20the%20scheme%20%E2%80%93%20one%20which%20the%20court%20has%20now%20held%20as%20violative%20of%20the%20right%20to%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20written%20submission%2C%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20said%20that%20citizens%E2%80%99%20right%20to%20know%20must%20be%20balanced%20with%20a%20person%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20privacy%20while%20donating%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20maintained%20that%20the%20citizens%20did%20not%20have%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgeneral%20right%20to%20know%20regarding%20the%20funding%20of%20political%20parties%E2%80%9D%2C%20and%20emphasised%20that%20%E2%80%98right%20to%20know%E2%80%99%20itself%20is%20not%20a%20general%20right%20available%20to%20citizens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20argued%20against%20the%20court%20examining%20the%20%E2%80%9Cinfluence%20of%20contributions%20by%20companies%20to%20political%20parties%E2%80%9D%2C%20calling%20it%20an%20issue%20of%20democratic%20significance%20that%20would%20be%20%E2%80%9Cbest%20left%20to%20the%20legislature.%E2%80%9D%20The%20Union%20also%20asked%20the%20court%20to%20exercise%20judicial%20restraint%20citing%20the%20legislation%E2%80%99s%20connection%20to%20economic%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20contended%20that%20the%20right%20of%20a%20buyer%20to%20purchase%20electoral%20bonds%20without%20having%20to%20disclose%20their%20political%20preferences%20ensured%20an%20individual%E2%80%99s%20right%20to%20privacy.%20The%20Union%20also%20told%20the%20court%20that%20%E2%80%9Canonymous%20political%20donations%E2%80%9D%20were%20a%20part%20of%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20concept%20of%20secret%20ballot%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdonating%20money%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20preferred%20party%20is%20a%20form%20of%20political%20self-expression%20that%20lies%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20privacy%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20Union%20did%20not%20distinguish%20between%20individuals%20and%20corporations%20while%20arguing%20for%20the%20right%20to%20privacy%20of%20citizens%20while%20buying%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectoral-bonds-are-illegal-now-but-who-benefited-for-the-6-years-they-lasted%5C%22%3EElectoral%20Bonds%20Are%20Illegal%20Now.%20But%20Who%20Benefitted%20for%20the%206%2B%20Years%20They%20Lasted%3F%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20fact%20that%20one%20party%20has%20received%20more%20support%20through%20donations%20than%20other%20parties%20cannot%20in%20itself%20be%20the%20legal%20grounds%20to%20challenge%20the%20Electoral%20Bond%20Scheme%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20government%20told%20the%20court.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ruling%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20(BJP)%20has%20been%20the%20net%20gainer%20of%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme.%20Of%20the%20total%20number%20of%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2012%2C008%20crore%20sold%20between%202017-2018%20and%202022-2023%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Felectoral-bonds-are-illegal-now-but-who-benefited-for-the-6-years-they-lasted%5C%22%3Ethe%20BJP%20received%20nearly%2055%25%20or%20Rs%206%2C564%20crore%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Meanwhile%2C%20Congress%20has%20received%20just%209.5%25%20of%20all%20bonds%20sold%20in%20the%20five-year%20period%20at%20Rs%201%2C135%20crore.%20The%20Trinamool%20Congress%20has%20received%20Rs%201%2C096%20crore%20from%20electoral%20bonds%20in%20this%20same%20time%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%2C%20while%20rejecting%20the%20Union%E2%80%99s%20argument%20in%20favour%20of%20exercising%20judicial%20restraint%20on%20account%20of%20the%20legislation%20being%20a%20part%20of%20%E2%80%9Ceconomic%20policy%E2%80%9D%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20court%20does%20not%20rely%20on%20ipse%20dixit%20%5Bassertion%5D%20of%20the%20government%2C%20that%20a%20legislation%20is%20an%20economic%20legislation.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20amendment%20to%20Section%2031%20of%20the%20RBI%20Act%20can%20be%20classified%20as%20a%20financial%20provision%E2%80%A6%20However%2C%20any%20resemblance%20to%20an%20economic%20policy%20ends%20there%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20court%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20amendment%20in%20question%20fall%20under%20the%20following%20two%20heads%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E1.%20Non-disclosure%20of%20information%20on%20electoral%20financing%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn2.%20Provisions%20permitting%20unlimited%20corporate%20funding%20to%20political%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20both%20accounts%2C%20the%20legislation%20relates%20to%20the%20electoral%20process%2C%20the%20court%20said%20as%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-electoral-bonds-quash-anonymous%5C%22%3Edeclared%20the%20electoral%20bond%20scheme%20as%20unconstitutional%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20its%20verdict%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707993917000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F01%2F10170626%2Fsyed-hussaini-HlLno-CSbq8-unsplash.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpart-of-secret-ballot-how-the-modi-govt-backed-electoral-bonds-in-the-supreme-court%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20had%20claimed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdonating%20money%20to%20one%E2%80%99s%20preferred%20party%20is%20a%20form%20of%20political%20self-expression%20that%20lies%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20privacy%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fpart-of-secret-ballot-how-the-modi-govt-backed-electoral-bonds-in-the-supreme-court%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BGuy%20Who%20Was%20Hosting%20Was%20Mean%26quot%3B%3A%20SRK%20On%20Turning%20Down%20Slumdog%20Millionaire%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22http