itizens'%20fundamental%20right%20to%20information.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felectoral-bonds-supreme-court-electoral-bonds-verdict-today-the-scheme-the-questions-and-the-defence-5060924%5C%22%3EElectoral%20bonds%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20a%20financial%20instrument%20that%20allows%20individuals%20and%20businesses%20to%20make%20anonymous%20donations%20to%20political%20parties.%20They%20were%20introduced%20by%20the%20BJP%20government%20in%202018%20as%20an%20alternative%20to%20cash%20donations.%20They%20were%20pitched%20as%20an%20initiative%20to%20bring%20transparency%20in%20political%20funding.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Election%20Commission%20data%2C%2028%2C030%20electoral%20bonds%20worth%20Rs%2016%2C437.63%20crore%20were%20sold%20between%202016%20and%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20was%20the%20primary%20beneficiary%20of%20these%20donations%20and%20received%20Rs%2010%2C122%20crore%2C%20nearly%2060%25%20of%20the%20total%20donations.%20The%20main%20opposition%20Congress%20party%20came%20a%20distant%20second%2C%20receiving%20Rs%201%2C547%20crore%20or%2010%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20same%20period%2C%20while%20West%20Bengal's%20ruling%20Trinamool%20Congress%20got%20Rs%20823%20crore%20or%208%20per%20cent%20of%20all%20electoral%20bonds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonations%20made%20to%20the%20BJP%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20were%20three%20times%20more%20than%20that%20of%20all%20other%2030%20parties%20combined%20on%20the%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20donations%20received%20by%20seven%20national%20parties%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%20are%20as%20follows%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%3A%20Rs%2010%2C122%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnCongress%3A%20Rs%201%2C547%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnTMC%3A%20Rs%20823%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnCPI(M)%3A%20Rs%20367%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnNCP%3A%20Rs%20231%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnBSP%3A%20Rs%2085%20crore%3Cbr%3E%5CnCPI%3A%20Rs%2013%20crore%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEC%20data%20also%20shows%20that%20from%202017%20to%202022%2C%20the%20BJP%20received%20over%20five%20times%20the%20donations%20through%20electoral%20bonds%20than%20the%20Congress%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20had%20been%20brought%20to%20curb%20black%20money%20and%20bring%20transparency%20into%20political%20donations%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20today%20said%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffinancial-support-to-political-parties-can-lead-to-quid-pro-quo-supreme-court-5061117%5C%22%3Eobjectives%20do%20not%20justify%20the%20scheme%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Additionally%2C%20it%20highlighted%20that%20alternative%20methods%20could%20effectively%20achieve%20these%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707989700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2022-01%2Flq9u46ag_bjp-generic-supporters-flag-pti_625x300_24_January_22.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-bonds-worth-rs-16-000-crore-sold-till-2022-who-got-how-much-5062408%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20is%20likely%20to%20be%20hit%20the%20hardest%20with%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20scrapping%20the%20electoral%20bonds%20scheme%2C%20as%20the%20party%20received%20over%2060%25%20of%20the%20donations%20made%20under%20the%20scheme%20between%202016-2022.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-bonds-worth-rs-16-000-crore-sold-till-2022-who-got-how-much-5062408%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-bonds-worth-rs-16-000-crore-sold-till-2022-who-got-how-much-5062408%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Felection-bonds-worth-rs-16-000-crore-sold-till-2022-who-got-how-much-5062408%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farooq%20Abdullah's%20Party%20To%20Fight%20Alone%20In%20J%26amp%3BK%20In%20Another%20Setback%20For%20