content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133759%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-15-at-1.36.06-PM.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20The%20legislation%20invoked%20by%20the%20Union%20government%20to%20give%20itself%20powers%20to%20block%20internet%20services%20in%20Punjab%20last%20week%20as%20farmers%20prepared%20to%20launch%20their%20protest%2C%20is%20a%20British-era%20law%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindu.com%2Fnews%2Fnational%2Fcentre-used-british-era-act-to-block-internet-in-punjab-ahead-of-the-farmers-march%2Farticle67846087.ece%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20the%20context%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20emergency%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cpublic%20safety%E2%80%9D%2C%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20invoked%20its%20powers%20under%20the%20Temporary%20Suspension%20of%20Telecom%20Services%20(Public%20Emergency%20or%20Public%20Safety)%20Rules%2C%202017%20of%20the%20Indian%20Telegraph%20Act%2C%201885%2C%20to%20suspend%20internet%20within%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%2020%20police%20stations%20in%20Patiala%2C%20SAS%20Nagar%2C%20Bathinda%2C%20Sri%20Mukhtsar%20Sahib%2C%20Mansa%2C%20Sangrur%20and%20Fatehgarh%20Sahib%20since%20last%20week%2C%20as%20per%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20noteworthy%20that%20a%20Punjab%20government%20official%20confirmed%20to%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20had%20the%20power%20to%20issue%20such%20orders%20under%20the%20Rules%20and%20that%20the%20Punjab%20government%20had%20not%20objected%20it.%20Meanwhile%2C%20the%20BJP-ruled%20Haryana%20government%20issued%20orders%20to%20suspend%20internet%20services%20in%20that%20particular%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fprsindia.org%2Fpolicy%2Freport-summaries%2Fsuspension-of-telecom-services-internet-and-its-impact%5C%22%3Ereport%20%3C%2Fa%3Esubmitted%20on%20December%202021%2C%20the%20parliamentary%20standing%20committee%20on%20communications%20and%20information%20technology%20had%20observed%20that%20internet%20shutdowns%20have%20implications%20on%20national%20economy%2C%20freedom%20of%20press%2C%20education%20and%20healthcare%20services.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CUnder%20the%202017%20Rules%2C%20telecom%2Finternet%20shutdowns%20may%20be%20ordered%20on%20grounds%20of%20public%20emergency%20and%20public%20safety.%20Public%20emergency%20and%20public%20safety%20have%20not%20been%20defined%20in%20the%201885%20Act%20or%20the%202017%20Rules%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Shashi%20Tharoor-led%20parliamentary%20committee%20report%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20a%20dozen%20accounts%20on%20X%20(formerly%20called%20Twitter)%20and%20Facebook%20which%20functioned%20as%20official%20pages%20of%20farmers%E2%80%99%20organisations%20and%20unions%20ahead%20of%20their%20%E2%80%98Delhi%20Chalo%E2%80%99%20protest%20have%20been%20withheld%20in%20India%20seemingly%20upon%20government%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffarmers-social-media-accounts-withheld-protest%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Agenda%20Is%20to%20Silence%20Us%E2%80%99%3A%20Key%20Social%20Media%20Accounts%20Withheld%2C%20Farmers%20Vow%20to%20Boycott%20Centre%E2%80%99s%20Meetings%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EX%20accounts%20and%20Facebook%20pages%20of%20prominent%20farmer%20leaders%20like%20Sarvan%20Singh%20Pandher%2C%20the%20coordinator%20of%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20Tejveer%20Singh%20Ambala%2C%20the%20spokesperson%20of%20BKU%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Ramandeep%20Singh%20Mann%2C%20Surjit%20Singh%20Phull%20from%20BKU%20Krantikari%2C%20farmer%20leader%20Harpal%20Sangha%2C%20Ashok%20Danoda%20from%20Haryana%20and%20many%20others%20have%20been%20withheld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20officials%20official%20pages%20which%20supported%20the%20movement%20and%20posted%20updates%20on%20it%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%C2%A0%20%40Tractor2twitr_P%20run%20by%20Bhavjit%20Singh%2C%20Bhartiya%20Kisan%20Union%20(Shaheed%20Bhagat%20Singh)%20and%20Progressive%20Farmers%20Front%2C%20run%20by%20Guramneet%20Singh%20Mangat%20%E2%80%93%20are%20also%20banned%20by%20the%20government.%20BKU%20(SBS)%20is%20one%20of%20the%20main%20farmer%20unions%20which%20was%20leading%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20from%20Ambala%2C%20Haryana.%20%E2%80%98Gaon%20Sawera%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20page%20run%20by%20independent%20journalist%20Mandeep%20Punia%20and%20his%20personal%20page%20has%20been%20withheld.%20Punia%20was%20arrested%20during%20the%202021%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707984664000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F15133759%2FScreen-Shot-2024-02-15-at-1.36.06-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-modi-government-used-british-era-law-to-give-itself-powers-to-suspend-internet%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20time%20the%20Union%20government%20suspended%20internet%20within%20the%20jurisdiction%20of%2020%20police%20stations%20in%20Patiala%2C%20SAS%20Nagar%2C%20Bathinda%2C%20Sri%20Mukhtsar%20Sahib%2C%20Mansa%2C%20Sangrur%20and%20Fatehgarh%20Sahib.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fagriculture%2Ffarmers-protest-modi-government-used-british-era-law-to-give-itself-powers-to-suspend-internet%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22HCL%20Tech%20makes%203%20days%20work%20from%20office%20compulsory%3A%20Read%20global%20HR%20head's%20email%20to%20employees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1707983518000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107715658%2Cimgsize-1374362.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fhcl-tech-makes-3-days-work-from-office-compulsory-read-glob