2F333558%2Fbest-farm-stays-in-india-with-natural-pool-organic-food-slow-travel%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20destination%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20choice.%20Armed%20with%20postcards%20that%20boasted%20the%20magnificent%20forts%20and%20camera%20pictures%20that%20showed%20off%20the%20colourful%20%3Cem%3Ebazaars%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20the%20couple%20was%20ready%20for%20more%20such%20authentic%20Rajasthani%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20stay%20in%20a%20Rajasthani%20home%20would%20be%20the%20icing%20on%20the%20cake.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20place%20they%20came%20across%20in%20Jodhpur%20was%20the%20village%20of%20Salawas%20which%20prides%20itself%20on%20the%20legendary%20%3Cem%3Edhurrie%3C%2Fem%3E%20making%20(handwoven%20floor%20coverings%20whose%20designs%20are%20inspired%20by%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20culture).%20Lucy%20could%20hardly%20contain%20her%20excitement%20on%20meeting%20Pukhraj%20ji%E2%80%99s%20family%20whose%20ancestors%20have%20been%20engaged%20in%20the%20artisanal%20craft%20for%20over%20seven%20centuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHours%20later%2C%20her%20arms%20were%20loaded%20with%20purchases%20of%20woven%20%3Cem%3Edhurries%20%3C%2Fem%3Efor%20her%20friends%20back%20home.%20It%20was%20time%20to%20leave.%20But%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F321695%2Faamir-khanyari-turned-ancestral-land-into-traditional-kashmir-homestay%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20rustic%20village%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20its%20mud%20homes%20and%20sprawling%20courtyards%20had%20cast%20a%20trance%20on%20her.%20She%20found%20it%20impossible%20to%20leave%20this%20vintage%20magic%20for%20the%20plushness%20of%20a%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Pukhraj%20ji%E2%80%99s%20son%20Chhotaram%20Prajapat%2C%20who%20is%20now%20in%20his%2030s%20recalls%2C%20the%20couple%20showed%20every%20intention%20to%20stay%20back%20with%20his%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20know%20English%20back%20t